dataIdInfo.idAbs: This polygon data layer represents hydrography for Oneida County, Wisconsin at year-end 2016. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Oneida_HydroPoly_YE2016.gdb.[This polygon feature class represents lakes, rivers, streams, drainages and other surface water.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp:
This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
[To manage the surface waters in Oneida County]
